! ENE Wiki Layer

A SQLite-backed wiki layer for revisions, links, categories, backlinks, and
deterministic write receipts.

!! Why It Matters

This is the bridge between full chat dumps, TiddlyWiki cards, and ENE-style
provenance. It lets wiki edits become inspectable records instead of loose
page changes.

